thread.title_full: Mexico cenbank sells $200 mln at 16.8453 pesos at daily auction | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Mexico cenbank sells $200 mln at 16.8453 pesos at daily auction
text: MEXICO CITY, Sept 1 The central bank of Mexico sold $200 million on Tuesday at an average price of 16.8453 pesos per dollar, the bank said, part of an auction program to boost foreign exchange liquidity following a slide in the peso. (Reporting by Christine Murray )
